Miss Yuan has great taste in men.

17
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:34,300
A real gift from the heavens.

18
00:02:34,370 --> 00:02:35,090
All right, go back to training.

19
00:03:08,830 --> 00:03:09,340
Up next,

20
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:11,230
you will undergo

21
00:03:11,410 --> 00:03:12,580
a ten-minute kidnapping exercise.

22
00:03:12,970 --> 00:03:14,170
When I blow my whistle,

23
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:15,770
turn around immediately and grab the piece of cloth.

24
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:17,460
After that,

25
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,060
find any opponent

26
00:03:19,370 --> 00:03:21,430
and tie him up.

27
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:22,930
Remember this.

28
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,870
You're forbidden from attacking your opponent's

29
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:26,829
joints and vital organs.

30
00:03:27,090 --> 00:03:28,680
You are free to use any other method

31
00:03:28,940 --> 00:03:29,720
to subdue your opponent.

32
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:31,560
Understood?

33
00:03:31,890 --> 00:03:33,010
Yes, Sir!

34
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,810
Stop yanking!

35
