38
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:24,850
You said you'd undergo the same training as these bodyguards.

39
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,110
Listen up.

40
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,090
As a bodyguard,

41
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:30,280
you have to sacrifice your dignity.

42
00:05:31,030 --> 00:05:32,560
Your employer's safety is your top priority.

43
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,650
Your self-image is secondary.

44
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:44,800
I'm harsher on you

45
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:47,130
because you're Chief Instructor Yuan's brother-in-law.

46
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:48,030
I'm not his brother-in-law.

47
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:48,930
I don't care!

48
00:05:49,610 --> 00:05:51,170
Since Mr. Yuan permitted you attend to this training camp,

49
00:05:51,370 --> 00:05:52,800
